description: Letter dated 08/02/2010 from Geoff Russell (Chief Executive, Learning and Skills Council) to Ashok Kumar MP regarding people under 20 years old in further education in (a) England, (b) the North East and (c) Middlesbrough and (d) Redcar and Cleveland constituency received assistance in meeting childcare costs from 2004 to 2009. Incl. table. 1 p.
department: Department for Children, Schools and Families
